The paper focuses on liver lesion detection using deep learning techniques, specifically convolutional neural networks (CNNs). This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves image processing and feature extraction, which are common topics in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM) research. Finally, the paper also discusses image registration and classification recognition, which are relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR).
